Text::Aligner

A module to align text.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

Alternatively, you should use your favourite CPAN client or distribution's
package manager.

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Text::Aligner

You can also look for information at:

    MetaCPAN
        http://metacpan.org/release/Text-Aligner

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Text::Aligner

